text: Parios (; literally "one who comes from (the island and/or city of) Paros, a Parian") is a Greek family name. Notable people with this name include: * Aqua Parios Fashion Model * Athanasios Parios (1722–1813), Greek hieromonk * Yiannis Parios (born 1946 ), Greek vocalist == References == Category:Greek- language surnames Category:Surnames
title: Parios
